## Arquitetura

### Monolito Modular DDD
```
API Layer         → Controllers, DTOs
Application Layer → Use Cases, Commands
Domain Layer      → Entidades, Value Objects (Java puro, sem Spring)
Infrastructure    → Repositories JPA, JWT, AI, Storage, Email
```

**Regra de dependência — nunca violar:**
```
API → Application → Domain ← Infrastructure
```

### Módulos
```
shared         → TenantContext, TenantAware, TenantEntityListener, Exceptions
identity       → AppUser, Role, Permission, JWT, RefreshToken, SecurityConfig
clients        → Client, Contact, Prescription, PrescriptionGrade, ClientAddress (Fase 2)
products       → Frame, FrameSku, LensType, LensGradeRange, ContactLens, Supplier
stock          → StockItem, StockMovement, PurchaseOrder
sales          → ServiceOrder, Sale, SaleItem, Payment
financial      → CashRegister, Transaction
notifications  → NotificationLog, jobs
reports        → relatórios por período
labels         → geração de PDF (OS e produto)
```

---

## Segurança

### Spring Security — stateless JWT
```java
http
  .csrf(AbstractHttpConfigurer::disable)
  .sessionManagement(s -> s.sessionCreationPolicy(STATELESS))
  .authorizeHttpRequests(auth -> auth
      .requestMatchers("/api/auth/**").permitAll()
      .requestMatchers("/actuator/health", "/actuator/prometheus").permitAll()
      .anyRequest().authenticated())
  .addFilterBefore(jwtAuthFilter, UsernamePasswordAuthenticationFilter.class)
```

### .env
- **NUNCA** commitar — deve estar no `.gitignore`
- Credentials expostas → revogar imediatamente nas plataformas
- Usar `.env.example` com valores fictícios

### JWT
```
Access token  → 1 hora
Refresh token → 7 dias, SHA-256 no banco, rotacionado a cada uso

Payload:
{
  "sub": "userId",
  "tenantId": "uuid",
  "branchId": "uuid",
  "role": "VENDOR",
  "permissions": ["sales:create"],
  "tokenVersion": 3
}

Token versioning: ao mudar permissões → tokenVersion++
JWT com versão diferente → 401 → força re-login
```

### Permissões `resource:action`
```
sales:create    sales:view      sales:cancel    sales:discount
clients:create  clients:view    clients:edit
stock:view      stock:edit      stock:purchase-order
cash:open       cash:close      cash:view
reports:view    labels:print    ai:read-prescription
users:manage    roles:configure notifications:view
```

### Papéis padrão (criados por tenant no cadastro)
| Papel | Permissões |
|---|---|
| OWNER | todas |
| MANAGER | todas exceto `users:manage` e `roles:configure` |
| VENDOR | sales, clients — sem cash, reports financeiros, administração |

---

## Observabilidade

```
Micrometer → /actuator/prometheus → Grafana Cloud free tier
(10k séries, 14 dias retenção — sem custo no servidor)

Endpoints expostos:
  /actuator/health      → liveness/readiness
  /actuator/prometheus  → métricas Prometheus

Métricas de negócio customizadas nos use cases:
  Counter: os.opened, ai.prescription.read, sale.confirmed
  Gauge:   plan.os.usage (% do limite mensal)
```

---

## Multi-tenancy

```
tenant_id em toda tabela operacional
TenantContext (ThreadLocal) populado pelo JwtAuthFilter
TenantContext.clear() sempre no finally
@PrePersist injeta tenant_id em todo INSERT
@PreUpdate valida que tenant_id não foi alterado
```

