## Padrões de Código

### Injeção por construtor — sempre
```java
// nunca @Autowired em campo
@Service
public class CreateServiceOrderUseCase {
    private final ServiceOrderRepository repository;
    private final StockService stockService;

    public CreateServiceOrderUseCase(
            ServiceOrderRepository repository,
            StockService stockService) {
        this.repository   = repository;
        this.stockService = stockService;
    }
}
```

### Records para VOs e DTOs
```java
public record PrescriptionGrade(Eye eye, BigDecimal spherical,
        BigDecimal cylindrical, int axis, BigDecimal addition) {
    public PrescriptionGrade {
        if (axis < 0 || axis > 180)
            throw new IllegalArgumentException("Axis must be between 0 and 180");
    }
}
```

### Swagger em interface separada
```java
// spec/ServiceOrderApi.java — só Swagger
@Tag(name = "Service Orders")
public interface ServiceOrderApi {
    @Operation(summary = "Open service order")
    ResponseEntity<ServiceOrderResponse> create(@RequestBody CreateServiceOrderRequest req);
}

// ServiceOrderController.java — só código
@RestController
public class ServiceOrderController implements ServiceOrderApi {
    @Override
    public ResponseEntity<ServiceOrderResponse> create(CreateServiceOrderRequest req) { ... }
}
```

### Idioma
```
Inglês   → código, variáveis, classes, pacotes, banco
Português → userMessage (erro ao usuário), docs ADR, README de módulo
```

---

## TDD

```
Red → Green → Blue
70% unitários (JUnit 5 + Mockito)
20% integração (Testcontainers)
10% API (MockMvc)

Nomenclatura:
  should_{behavior}_when_{condition}
  should_preserve_delivery_address_when_client_deletes_it()
  should_reject_token_when_version_mismatch()
  should_reserve_stock_when_service_order_is_opened()
```

---

## Exceções

```java
BusinessRuleException            → 422
ResourceNotFoundException        → 404
PermissionDeniedException        → 403
PlanLimitException               → 402
InvalidStatusTransitionException → 422
InsufficientStockException       → 422
TenantInactiveException          → 402
InvalidTokenException            → 401
SecurityViolationException       → 403
```

